GET & TRY
---------
https://github.com/bluebat/tksimsys

	tar xvf tksimsys-*.*.tar.gz
	cd tksimsys-*.*

There should be wish4.0 or higher (http://www.scriptics.com/) and 
better also ghostview (http://www.cs.wisc.edu/~ghost/ghostview/) installed.
then:

	wish tksimsys.tcl -- -bmdir bitmaps &


INSTALL
-------
You may change something in the Makefile and tksimsys.tcl
then type:

	make
	make install

and run:

	tksimsys

